          <p class='first-para'>
            Will my hon. Friend give way?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0377P0_20011218_WH_58'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-stewart' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0377P0_20011218_WH_58' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Stewart' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
